## 🧠 About The Project

VibeNet is a full-stack social networking platform built to let users share photos, discover trends, and express themselves through a visual feed. Inspired by platforms like Instagram, VibeNet brings community vibes to life through images, captions, likes, and follows.

![VibeNet Screenshot](assets/vibenet_screenshot.png)

---

## 🚀 Features

- 📷 Photo Upload and Sharing
- 📰 Real-Time Social Feed
- 💬 Comment and Like System
- 🧑‍🤝‍🧑 Follow/Unfollow Users
- 🔎 Explore Trending Posts
- 🔐 User Authentication
- 🖼️ User Profile Pages
- 🌙 Light/Dark Mode Toggle

---

## 🛠️ Built With

- *Frontend*: HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, Bootstrap
- *Backend*: Node.js, Express.js
- *Database*: MongoDB
- *Authentication*: JWT, bcrypt
- *Storage*: Cloudinary / LocalStorage (for images)

---

## 🧰 Getting Started

To get a local copy up and running follow these simple steps:

### Prerequisites

- Node.js
- MongoDB

### Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/sharugowda-123/VibeNet-Project.git
cd VibeNet-Project
npm install
npm start
